    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>and <strong>salt </strong>and mix it all together</p>",
