    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong>, <strong>halved green beans</strong> and <strong>cashew nuts</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for an initial 10-12 min</p><p>After the initial 10 min, remove the lid and cook for a final 4-5 min – this is your<strong> mixed vegetable curry</strong></p>",
